final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Align the agent on the horizontal axis (y=8) since it's already aligned. Next, move the agent to pick up the yellow key by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=5 and the key is at x=13, it must move RIGHT 13 - 5 = 8 times. Then, while holding the Key, move the agent to reach the cyan KeyDoor (x=18) by moving RIGHT again. Because the agent will be at x=13 after picking up the Key, it must move RIGHT 18 - 13 = 5 times. This action will open the KeyDoor and destroy the Key. Finally, move the agent to reach the goal (x=19, y=9) by moving UP once and then moving RIGHT once.
